Structure:
-NNBComponent
    -NNBBlock
        -NNBLayer
            -NNBResizableLayer
                -NNBAffineLayer (1D)
                -NNBConvLayer   (2D)
                -NNBPoolingLayer
                -NNBFlattenLayer
            -NNBVectorizedLayer
                -NNB1DVectorizedLayer
                -NNB2DVectorizedLayer
        -NNBCostFuncBlock
        -NNBRegularizer
    -NNBNeuron
        -NNB1DNeuron
        -NNB2DNeuron
    -NNBConnection
        -NNBSimConnection
        -NNBConvConnection
        -NNBRegConnection
-NNBForm
    -NNBComboBoxForm
-NNBAnimation
-NNBScene


